            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44026548">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44026548/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p44026548-3.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">所以序言算原文么？我只是记录一下未来可能要阅读的一些作家的名字。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-16 22:23</span>
                  
